e find that on average, SMBHs are not rapidly\nspinning during accretion. Finally, using an independent measurement of\nEddington ratios, we estimate the SMBH e-folding time for the brightest AGNs\n(quasars) to be <tau> =100+151-60 Myr.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Oct 2008 20:05:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-02-11"}
